set up the .env file to run with your system with the database connection you use

then run composer install
then run npm install for the styling and use tailwind

then run php artisan key:generate to generate the APP_KEY encryption key

if all is ok
create database with the name 'blog' , run php artisan migrate --seed to seed the admin info to login with

when migration is ok , use your localhost url 'http://your_localhost_url/admin' to access the admin panel

you can use this info to login
email: admin@gmail.com
password: 123123123

